This paper is about developing a novel method for providing unexpected recommendations in recommender systems. The paper focuses on modeling user expectations in the latent space rather than in the feature space. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is Information Retrieval (cs.IR), which deals with the retrieval of information from large datasets. Other likely sub-categories include Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), as these areas are closely related to the development of recommender systems and the analysis of large datasets.
